        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Declarations&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Non-solicitation whilst on NHS Premises&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You agree that whilst on Assignment you shall not approach anyone employed by the NHS to suggest them become employed or engaged by Blue Arrow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Confidentiality&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You agree you shall not disclose to any person, other than a person authorised by the NHS, nor use for your own or any other person’s benefit any information acquired in connection with your Assignment or the NHS generally or its arrangements with Blue Arrow. Further you shall not disclose to any person other than a person authorised by the NHS nor use for your own or any other person’s benefit any information concerning:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Authority, its staff or its procedures;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The identity of any patient under the care of the Authority;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The medical condition of or the treatment received by any patient.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Investigation, Prosecution Statement &amp;amp; Suspension&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a Blue Arrow Employee you shall advise (and shall use all reasonable endeavours to ensure that you shall advise) us in writing if you are or ever have been under investigation or prosecution relating to a conviction, or which could lead to a conviction, after the most recent DBS check was undertaken or you are currently or have been subject to any kind of investigation be either an NHS body, or other wider public sector body, or the relevant professional and regulatory body.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Data Protection&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Blue Arrow may from time to time disclose personal data or information held about you to The NHS bodies including but not limited to your personal details, employment and education history and references or other personal data obtained about you from third parties&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Final Statement&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;I confirm I understand and agree to abide by all the information and instructions Blue Arrow has provided to me in this NHS Agency Worker Handbook (V1 – Oct 21) and under my Terms of Engagement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Candidate Signed Name: &lt;/b&gt;{!Get_Candidate.FirstName} {!Get_Candidate.LastName}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Candidate Signed Date/Time:&lt;/b&gt; {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}&lt;/p&gt;</text>
